Avid Technology, Inc. is another significant player in the audio and video editing software market, offering renowned products such as Media Composer and Pro Tools. These solutions are widely used in the media and entertainment industry for their robust editing capabilities and professional-grade features. Avid's long-standing presence in the market and its reputation for delivering high-quality software have solidified its position as a preferred choice for industry professionals and organizations looking for reliable editing solutions.

Corel Corporation has established itself as a key player in the video editing software segment with products like Corel VideoStudio. Known for its user-friendly interface, intuitive editing tools, and creative effects, Corel VideoStudio caters to both beginners and experienced editors seeking a comprehensive editing solution. Corel's focus on providing a range of editing capabilities while maintaining ease of use has garnered a loyal customer base and positioned the company as a credible competitor in the market.

